Package idlreasonerchoco.configuration

Class IDLConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • idlreasonerchoco.configuration.IDLConfiguration
  • public class IDLConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
    IDLConfiguration setups IDL configurations. It configures specification type, API specification, operation path, and operation type.
